# VLAN Design

## Overview

To improve security, reduce broadcast traffic, and simplify network management, the GreenFields Logistics Ltd. network is segmented into multiple Virtual Local Area Networks (VLANs).

Each department is assigned a dedicated VLAN based on its operational requirements.

