# Design Principles

The VLAN design follows these principles:

- Department-based segmentation
- Reduced broadcast domains
- Improved network security
- Easier troubleshooting
- Better scalability
- Support for future expansion

---

# Security Considerations

- Finance and HR VLANs are isolated from Guest Wi-Fi.
- CCTV devices communicate only with the Network Video Recorder (NVR).
- Servers are hosted in a dedicated VLAN.
- Network management traffic is restricted to authorized administrators.
- Guest Wi-Fi users have Internet-only access.

---

# Expected Benefits

- Enhanced security
- Improved performance
- Simplified administration
- Reduced broadcast traffic
- Better fault isolation
